      "asbval:note": "Paper does not describe or mention an 'mspToLib' function, .msp-to-CSV conversion with ionization mode suffixes, or any automated conversion pipeline from .msp format. The paper states libraries were 'adapted from those of the LipidMatch R package' and 'generated from experimental CID MS/MS spectra from proton or sodium adducts...deposited in MassBank and GNPS databases' but does not detail a conversion process with mode-annotation suffixes. No such function or workflow is documented in the passages.",
