      "asbval:note": "Paper describes ranked output generation but does not explicitly name a function called 'annotateRC()'. The paper references RAMClustR objects and XCMS processing but the specific function name 'annotateRC' is not found in passages. The workflow performs the described function but the function name may be inaccurate or from supplementary material not provided.",
