      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms MetaboAnnotatoR is an R package, but does not specify R version 4.5.0 or higher as a requirement. The paper does not mention 'genFragEntry' function or its specific version requirements.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1021-acs-analchem-1c03032",
