      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": null,
      "asbval:note": "Paper does not mention 'genFragEntry' function, 'noise=0.005' parameter, or 'mpeaksThres=0.1' parameter. MetaboAnnotatoR uses correlation threshold \u03b8 (default 0.8) for pseudo-MS/MS generation and occurrence scores for fragment matching, not the named parameters in the card.",
