      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Precision and recall values of 82-92% and 82-85%, respectively, were obtained for features found in the highest-rank scores (1-5). These results equal or outperform those obtained using MS-DIAL software, the current state of the art for AIF data annotation.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper demonstrates improved annotation specificity and precision through its filtering approach, though the mechanism is correlation-based rather than explicit SNR thresholding.",
