    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/pseudo-ms-ms-spectra-ranking-and-curation/004",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Two R packages, CAMERA10 and RAMClustR,5 can also be used to reconstruct in-source parent-fragment pseudo-MS/MS spectra... A random selection of 100 LC\u2013MS AIF chromatograms from both Lipid+ and Lipid\u2013 as well as HILIC+ datasets from the MESA cohort was processed in R using XCMS23 version 3.4.4 and RAMClustR package5 to obtain pseudo-MS/MS spectra (dataset-wide reconstruction)",
      "asbval:note": "RAMClustR confirmed as generating pseudo-MS/MS spectra; integration with XCMS confirmed.",
