      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Graphical outputs contain, for each ranked result, the pseudo-MS/MS spectrum comprising the matched peaks and the corresponding EICs; and for each target feature, the pseudo-MS/MS and pseudo-MS (MS1 spectrum containing all ions correlated to the target feature) spectra and the corresponding EICs are stored for later inspection.",
      "asbval:note": "The paper explicitly describes visual inspection of pseudo-MS/MS spectra with matched peaks and ranked candidates as part of the workflow output and validation process.",
